{"tid":1817463,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【和你 Shop 極可能是警察卧底所設置的圍捕陷阱】","createTime":"2020-01-09T06:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T00:45:50.000Z","uid":270077,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b50b0108120c0014a613a4dd3399c7bd6ee0dc","tid":1817463,"uid":270077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"疑點：<br />\n（1）所選地點絕大部分是中共直接管轄的商場（新鴻基／港鐵）；<br />\n（2）新鴻基地產（去年九月委任黨員成為董事）旗下的新城市廣場在用和你 Shop 前刻意用鐵鍊鎖上所有走火通道；<br />\n（3）消防人員（疑被警方操控）巡視後扮視而不見；<br />\n（4）投訴人要求消防員到場複檢解除封鎖後翌日再次全部上鎖；<br />\n（5）和你 Shop 當日大量年青人無路可逃而被捕／消失。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">神啊，願你賜下智慧，讓抗爭者成功避開警察所設置的圍捕陷阱。</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/LLocDi7tUoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLLocDi7tUoI&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF069osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=c3a7a257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LLocDi7tUoI</a></div>"},{"pid":"a15e5e67387dcd6fdf6e48f0659e9587d789c8cc","tid":1817463,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"唔知比咩反應你好.....地點係班狗簡既咩"},{"pid":"a890d9ed198f7939aad826ff4a69ecab611b78ef","tid":1817463,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:45:50.000Z","msg":"請問你對蕭生建議認為對不對我有什麼和其他建議?<br />\n你會唔會推行他的建議?<br />\n給香港人的一封家書〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉2020-01-08<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=abAzM_e3RY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DabAzM_e3RY&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF069osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=6896bc53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=abAzM_e3RY</a>"}]}